Create function to convert dataframe into time series

to_xts = function(df) {
  #Convert UK Engergy data into xts
  return(xts(as.numeric(as.character(df[,4])),order.by=as.POSIXct(as.character(df[,3]), format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', tz="GMT")))
}
